{"repo": {"name": {"en-US": "Cacing69 Repository"}, "description": {"en-US": "Personal F-Droid repository for experimental and production Android apps."}, "icon": {"en-US": {"name": "/icons/icon.png", "sha256": "e5bce01341df61aa1e86ea63c33cbf122b81a02270a1747d102e147c85dca42a", "size": 578847}}, "address": "https://cacing69.github.io/f-droid/repo", "timestamp": 1778949482000, "categories": {"Development": {"name": {"en-US": "Development"}}, "Finance": {"name": {"en-US": "Finance"}}, "Internet": {"name": {"en-US": "Internet"}}, "Security": {"name": {"en-US": "Security"}}, "f-droid": {"name": {"en-US": "f-droid"}}}}, "packages": {"d93be65ad121e9771889578f35e48410135c1b170bf6f0a572fcea1341aaf99e": {"metadata": {"added": 1778949482000, "categories": ["f-droid"], "lastUpdated": 1778949482000, "name": {"en-US": ".DS_Store"}}, "versions": {"d93be65ad121e9771889578f35e48410135c1b170bf6f0a572fcea1341aaf99e": {"added": 1778949482000, "file": {"name": "/.DS_Store", "sha256": "d93be65ad121e9771889578f35e48410135c1b170bf6f0a572fcea1341aaf99e", "size": 6148}, "manifest": {"versionName": "d93be65", "versionCode": 0}}}}, "dev.cacing69.curel": {"metadata": {"added": 1778949480000, "categories": ["Internet", "Development", "Security"], "issueTracker": "https://github.com/cacing69/curel/issues", "lastUpdated": 1778949481000, "sourceCode": "https://github.com/cacing69/curel", "webSite": "https://cacing69.github.io/", "screenshots": {"phone": {"en-US": [{"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel/en-US/phoneScreenshots/01.jpeg", "sha256": "3f357cb91ca914ba4d38d744e4c05bf711365424d679bcd9f7306b0f49e650eb", "size": 96313}, {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel/en-US/phoneScreenshots/02.jpeg", "sha256": "3a3768d0a7834d160addd04e4506d3c2ce1640bb4c758a91f4e783af9a62e466", "size": 138144}, {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel/en-US/phoneScreenshots/03.jpeg", "sha256": "c7624e76e2f4e87a33de4b77c8bae8bee806ee2b47f19d5325f08b661b8b110e", "size": 38115}, {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel/en-US/phoneScreenshots/04.jpeg", "sha256": "40d5d2db3868a517c13b57cc80350c5eee78a0734f138c55b61377f38e3bb16d", "size": 136248}]}}, "name": {"en-US": "Curel"}, "summary": {"en-US": "Free, open-source, git-native curl workspace — local-first HTTP client"}, "description": {"en-US": "A free, open-source, git-native curl workspace. Local-first — your data stays on your device, synced through your own git repositories. No cloud, no accounts, no tracking.\n\nFeatures:\n\nHTTP Client:\n- Paste and execute curl commands\n- Request builder for constructing HTTP requests visually\n- Curl cheat sheet with syntax-highlighted examples\n- Support for common curl flags: -L, -v, --data, --data-raw, -o, -O, --trace, --trace-ascii, --connect-timeout, --max-time, -k\n- Syntax-highlighted response with JSON prettify\n- Search within response with match highlighting\n- HTML preview tab\n- Verbose output with DNS lookup, TLS info, and redirect chain\n- Trace output with hex dump format\n- Save response to file\n\nEnvironments:\n- Environment variables with <<VAR>> syntax and purple highlighting\n- Multiple environments with quick switch from action bar\n- Layered env resolution: project env > global env > undefined warning\n- Import/export environments as JSON\n- Secure variable storage (Keychain/Keystore)\n\nProjects & Organization:\n- Filesystem-first project organization\n- Save and open requests with folder support\n- Request drawer with search, rename, and delete\n- Status code badges from request metadata\n- Custom workspace location\n\nGit Sync:\n- Sync projects to GitHub, GitLab, or Gitea repositories (self-hosted supported)\n- Pull, push, and combined sync with 3-layer safety (optimistic lock, delete propagation, fast-forward check)\n- Conflict detection and resolution (pull overwrite / push overwrite)\n- Sync status indicators across the UI\n- Connect/disconnect git per project\n\nSettings & Theme:\n- Configurable User-Agent, connect-timeout, and max-time\n- Dracula theme with flat, no-shadow terminal design\n- Share curl command via system share sheet\n"}, "icon": {"en-US": {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel/en-US/icon_w0jtqtRGqNDN7PRM8L0GOr42uYcFqzO_2kuWrbwt24I=.png", "sha256": "c348edaad446a8d0cdecf44cf0bd063abe36b98705ab33bfda4b96adbc2ddb82", "size": 1063221}}, "preferredSigner": "251b142020e72938df647f22a373b93d9240ba3cbcd232f86772ad9007564a44"}, "versions": {"79a127eaad29567dbb79fd02eb07324c012b54d416c45c15d21a2786a59d67f7": {"added": 1778949481000, "file": {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel-x86_64.apk", "sha256": "79a127eaad29567dbb79fd02eb07324c012b54d416c45c15d21a2786a59d67f7", "size": 25792599}, "manifest": {"nativecode": ["x86_64"], "versionName": "1.5.0", "versionCode": 14500, "usesSdk": {"minSdkVersion": 24, "targetSdkVersion": 36}, "signer": {"sha256": ["251b142020e72938df647f22a373b93d9240ba3cbcd232f86772ad9007564a44"]}, "usesPermission": [{"name": "android.permission.INTERNET"}, {"name": "dev.cacing69.curel.DYNAMIC_RECEIVER_NOT_EXPORTED_PERMISSION"}]}}, "5e995c9eb8582eb94d105f3073004ef0df7b34a8dbc6fd72ab8df46727d40fcb": {"added": 1778949480000, "file": {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel-arm64-v8a.apk", "sha256": "5e995c9eb8582eb94d105f3073004ef0df7b34a8dbc6fd72ab8df46727d40fcb", "size": 24169254}, "manifest": {"nativecode": ["arm64-v8a"], "versionName": "1.5.0", "versionCode": 12500, "usesSdk": {"minSdkVersion": 24, "targetSdkVersion": 36}, "signer": {"sha256": ["251b142020e72938df647f22a373b93d9240ba3cbcd232f86772ad9007564a44"]}, "usesPermission": [{"name": "android.permission.INTERNET"}, {"name": "dev.cacing69.curel.DYNAMIC_RECEIVER_NOT_EXPORTED_PERMISSION"}]}}, "ff82d15d949b0892bcbddbb1410b3c263f39915dab09d15faa059eafc406ca52": {"added": 1778949481000, "file": {"name": "/dev.cacing69.curel-armeabi-v7a.apk", "sha256": "ff82d15d949b0892bcbddbb1410b3c263f39915dab09d15faa059eafc406ca52", "size": 21762612}, "manifest": {"nativecode": ["armeabi-v7a"], "versionName": "1.5.0", "versionCode": 11500, "usesSdk": {"minSdkVersion": 24, "targetSdkVersion": 36}, "signer": {"sha256": ["251b1